{"tid":1815343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（轉）馬路地面驚現簡體字？","createTime":"2020-01-07T12:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T08:25:12.000Z","uid":242025,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e4dd638e873dc43cc8c1ef41590b36fb7deb2d","tid":1815343,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wZxAsKJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwZxAsKJ.jpg&h=25adb04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1252628151428934/posts/3602602229764836/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1252628151428934%2Fposts%2F3602602229764836%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TfsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=979ed93c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1252628151428934/posts/3602602229764836/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n今朝西貢區議員何偉航 Stanley HO Wai-hong post 左張相，發現路面上出現「灣」字嘅「簡體字」。大家都好自然會覺得係咪又係搞赤化，強行消滅繁體字。  <br />\n<br />\n無錯，捍衞繁體字係我地嘅責任；不過其實路面上呢個疑似簡體字，其實係「繁體俗字」。因爲漢字變化多端，有舊式寫法之餘，仲有異體、俗寫。例如「台湾大哥大」用「湾」就係俗字嘅一種。  <br />\n<br />\n⭐️咁係唔係赤化？⭐️ <br />\n呢個情況下就唔係咁講。因爲二十年前，馬路上嘅「灣」都係咁寫；佢唔係標準嘅簡體字，因爲個「亦」字兩筆上下掉轉咗。如果你以前有留意開路面，或者都會有印象。係 1998 年杜老誌道天橋交通意外中，（畫面比較矇糊，但原諒我搵唔到一張更加淸晰嘅圖片🙏🙇🏻&zwj;♂️），「港灣道」個「湾」字就已經係咁寫～  <br />\n<br />\n⭐️咁好地地做咩寫「俗字」？⭐️ <br />\n呢層其實佢地唔係故意寫簡體字，而係因爲綫條比較粗嘅關係，寫唔到太複雜嘅字。因爲近年路面文字改用較幼嘅綫條，所以好多地方嘅「灣」字改返標準繁體寫法，舊式俗寫就買少見少喇。  <br />\n<br />\n⭐️道路硏究社嘅回應⭐️ <br />\n雖個「湾」字唔係簡體字，而係舊式俗字。但係我地都認爲，用返標準繁體寫法最好，始終大家習慣依家個寫法。  <br />\n<br />\n⭐️延伸閱讀⭐️ <br />\n【維基百科】繁體俗字 <br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/繁體俗字\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E7%B9%81%E9%AB%94%E4%BF%97%E5%AD%97&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TfsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=68b8441b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/繁體俗字</a>  <br />\n<br />\n【東方日報影片】杜老誌道天橋交通意外（影片一開始） <br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20140615/00176_097.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140615%2F00176_097.html&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TfsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=2bb68185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20140615/00176_097.html</a><br />\n<br />\n  #簡體字 #俗字"},{"pid":"83195b9cb427b24c52c60fe10de2672c17489601","tid":1815343,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:31:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c2290db98071507737474048e394f076c82419e","tid":1815343,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:31:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d4c1461a1f60fd7c6d075d7a213e284272a6cbe","tid":1815343,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:31:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22c93d6ef17461a25748f8e314ca40dfae744dcc","tid":1815343,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:32:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d71294458c0c65057043d552fb409e878cc20ac6","tid":1815343,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:32:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c300384f44b58181b27e71c21d3aab5d5413c3d","tid":1815343,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6cb6ecc27998dfb5524dcddf960628d34c38ee79","tid":1815343,"uid":242025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:36:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"519d859cd12540b9a311c808ae82c8d987c255a8","tid":1815343,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"98咪97之後<br />\n咪回歸咗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76057da87250afe6a96216cded83db859b85033b","tid":1815343,"uid":224561,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:36:30.000Z","msg":"個水字幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s